snippet.title: I bought SLUTBOX by Amber Rose AUGUST 2019 so u don't have to! Unboxing & Try On!!
snippet.description:
YOWSA!! Well this was my 1st Adult themed subscription box. It's not  September's but August 2019 Slutbox (ships late in the month) As a beauty box it's actually okay, not the worst I've seen this year but as an Adult themed subscription box it's woefully lacking. I unboxed and tried most of the products.

PS Sorry I've been MIA for a minute, life keeps throwing me curve balls, hopefully I can stay dodging and get back to regular uploads.

Here's Chrissy's Channel:

Chrissy Harless: Sub Boxes & Beauty: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCT3o7Hn75VAPK-9NlMBmyAw
